[24/07/2017 14:24:48] <font color="#00ff00">los 11 kilómetros</font>
[24/07/2017 14:24:51] <font color="#00ff00">que nos separan de las famosas</font>
[24/07/2017 14:24:51] <font color="#00ff00">cuevas Jenolan,</font>
